  "instructions": [
    "Heat coconut oil in a Dutch oven over medium heat until melted.",
    "Add diced carrot, zucchini, and bell pepper, sauté for 3 minutes.",
    "Stir in diced tomato, grated ginger, and lemon zest, cooking another 2 minutes.",
    "Pour in white wine and allow it to reduce by half, about 3 minutes.",
    "Add miso paste, low-sodium vegetable broth, and almond milk, stir until miso dissolves.",
    "Mix in rolled oats, bring the mixture to a simmer, cover, and cook for 12 minutes.",
    "Remove the lid, stir gently, and let the tagine thicken to a creamy consistency.",
    "Season with salt and pepper to taste, then serve hot with fresh herbs."
